text: This Musinsa Standard oversized blazer is the perfect fall OOTD piece. Fits my curvy body type so well with high-waisted wide leg pants. The wool blend material feels premium for 89000 won. Giving old money aesthetic vibes. Available on Musinsa and Zigzag.
author: style_diary

text: Comparing Nike Dunk Low vs New Balance 550 for daily wear. The NB550 has better arch support and the cream colorway goes with everything. Nike runs narrow for wide feet. Both around 139000 won on Kream. #sneakerhead #fitcheck
author: kicks_review
